[ValidTrueComment]:
The system does not adequately audit account creation events.

Remediation:
1. Install auditd: apt install auditd audispd-plugins
2. Enable and start: systemctl enable --now auditd
3. Add audit rules for account files:
   auditctl -w /etc/passwd -p wa -k identity
   auditctl -w /etc/shadow -p wa -k identity
   auditctl -w /etc/group -p wa -k identity
   auditctl -w /etc/gshadow -p wa -k identity
   auditctl -w /etc/security/opasswd -p wa -k identity
4. Make persistent: add rules to /etc/audit/rules.d/identity.rules
5. Reload: augenrules --load

Contact the system administrator to configure audit rules for account management files.

