[ValidTrueComment]:
The system does not provide centralized audit review capabilities.

Remediation:
1. Configure rsyslog for remote forwarding in /etc/rsyslog.conf:
   *.* @@siem-server.example.com:514
2. Install audit tools: apt install auditd audispd-plugins
3. Verify aureport/ausearch available: which aureport ausearch
4. For systemd journal forwarding: apt install systemd-journal-remote
5. Configure /etc/systemd/journal-upload.conf with central server URL
6. Restart services: systemctl restart rsyslog auditd

Centralized review enables correlation of events across system components.

