MFA for network access to non-privileged accounts is not deployed. No local PAM MFA modules detected and the XO auth-ldap plugin is not active.

Remediation Options:
Option A  Enable AD/LDAP authentication delegation (Recommended):
(1) Install and configure the XO auth-ldap plugin
