[ValidTrueComment]:
The system does not properly audit logon attempts.

Remediation:
1. Install auditd: apt install auditd
2. Ensure PAM audit module: verify pam_loginuid.so in /etc/pam.d/login and /etc/pam.d/sshd
3. Add logon watch rules:
   auditctl -w /var/log/faillog -p wa -k logins
   auditctl -w /var/log/lastlog -p wa -k logins
   auditctl -w /var/log/tallylog -p wa -k logins
4. Make persistent: augenrules --load

