[ValidTrueComment]:
The system does not adequately record user access start/end times.

Remediation:
1. Install auditd: apt install auditd audispd-plugins
2. Enable service: systemctl enable --now auditd
3. Verify wtmp logging: last -F -n 5
4. Ensure PAM session tracking in /etc/pam.d/common-session:
   session required pam_loginuid.so
   session required pam_lastlog.so showfailed
5. Add session rules to /etc/audit/rules.d/logins.rules:
   -w /var/log/wtmp -p wa -k logins
   -w /var/log/btmp -p wa -k logins
   -w /var/run/utmp -p wa -k logins
6. Reload: augenrules --load

