   -a always,exit -F arch=b32 -S open,openat,creat,truncate,ftruncate -F exit=-EPERM -F auid&gt;=1000 -F auid!=4294967295 -k access
4. Reload: augenrules --load
5. Verify: auditctl -l | grep access

