[ValidTrueComment]:
The system does not adequately audit account lifecycle events.

Remediation:
1. Install auditd: apt install auditd audispd-plugins
2. Enable service: systemctl enable --now auditd
3. Add account watch rules to /etc/audit/rules.d/identity.rules:
